{"word":"ἐπημοιβός","slug":"ἐπημοιβός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπημοιβός</b></el> <el>(ἐπ-ημοιβός, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμείβω'><el>ἀμείβω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>alternating, crossing</i>, of door-bolts, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>serving for change</i>, <el>χιτῶνες</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}